com.hazelcast.spi

Interface ManagedService

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AtomicLongService, AtomicReferenceService, CountDownLatchService, CRDTReplicationMigrationService, IdGeneratorService, LockServiceImpl, PNCounterService, SemaphoreService

    public interface ManagedService
    An interface that can be implemented by an SPI Service to receive lifecycle calls:
    1. initialization
    2. shutdown
    3. reset
